== nginx + gunicorn

Here some example scripts/config files for running PyLucid with nginx + gunicorn.

* nginx [engine x] is an HTTP and reverse proxy server.
* Gunicorn 'Green Unicorn' is a Python WSGI HTTP Server for UNIX.

There exist many viariants how to "run" a django web applications. Here we startup
the PyLucid WSGI process with gunicorn.sh and nginx will serve the static files
and communicates with gunicorn via unix sockets. 

